originalText.text: My Girlfriend and I loved staying here on our first trip to NYC! There were sweet treats on the way in every day that we admittedly took advantage of every day, there was water in our Suite, and the service was very clean and friendly! I cannot recommend this place enough. The house itself is just gorgeous and we could not believe how lucky we were to stay in a home like this… from the windows, to the rugs, to the architecture that’s been preserved- it was just so special. Thank you to everyone who works here in assisting making this experience alive.
